  "title": "Digital Media Operator (Negotiable salary )",
  "description": "<p>To partake in Cosmo5's growth, we are looking for the next superstar Media Operator to join the Cosmo5 Singapore Team. </p><p>As a key member of our team, you will collaborate with clients and internal stakeholders to develop, execute, and oversee effective media strategies that drive client success. You will be responsible for the day-to-day management of media campaigns, and supporting the account manager and client lead across key client deliverables.  </p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><p>💻 Digital Media Campaign Management: </p><ul><li><p>Support the account manager and client lead in planning, organising and developing all clients' deliverables. </p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Create and Optimise Digital Media campaigns across Google, Meta, TikTok, Pinterest, YouTube, Teads, Spotify, DOOH, etc..</p></li><li><p>Work on campaign pacing, adjusting budget, estimating monthly costs and reconciling discrepancies.</p></li><li><p>Track, report and analyse campaign performance</p></li><li><p>Research and implement digital advertising recommendations</p></li><li><p>Execute tests, collect and analyse data, identify trends and insights to achieve your client’s objectives</p></li></ul><p>💫 Client Management</p><ul><li><p>Present weekly and monthly reports to the clients’ teams, including campaign results, competitive data, learnings and recommendations. </p></li><li><p>Serve as the client's key point of contact for day to day tasks relating to campaigns, deliver client reporting, and analyse media campaign results.</p></li><li><p>Participate in meetings with key stakeholders to discuss strategy, objectives, and action plans. </p></li></ul><p>🚀 Internal</p><p><ul><li>Stay abreast of new technologies, tools, research and best practices in the digital marketing space</li><li>Complete regular training sessions and enrol in the Cosmo5 Academy.</li><li>Contribute to our Innovation Room by sharing your latest experiments and learnings monthly with the team.</li></ul><p></p></p><p><strong></strong></p>",
